<TITLE>
Malsum the Wolf (Malsom, Molsem)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Malsum (Molsem),
said to be a villainous wolf character in the folklore of the Wabanaki tribes.">
